The evidence with the title 'The mellowing of Maxine Waters ' says May 11, 2013  ... OVER her 22 years in Congress , Maxine Waters has likened bank executives to “ gangsters, ” snarkily addressed them as “ captains of the universe ” and threatened to tax their companies “ out of business. ”The Democrat from Los Angeles, in other words, is not known for showing love to the financial industry. 
